name: in Real Time
description:
[prod sascha]
I channeled these vocals on a radio shack mic after hiding my voice for some Time
the day after recording I discovered my cactus plant had bloomed overnight
these rare flowers bloom at night for one night only
this symbolic moment affirmed an astrologically significant Time of personal re(Birth) 
I am grateful to mint this 1of1 piece as proof of the multidimensional power of Love in my Life 
& the consistent thread of inspiration that Nature's spherical processes n rhythms have sewn into my artistry
thank you for Seeing me
in gratitude, 
R
